%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20spate%20of%20divorces%20among%20China's%20richest%20is%20forcing%20the%20securities%20regulator%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20large%20share%20sales%20following%20the%20breakups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224246%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20pose%20for%20wedding%20photos%20on%20the%20historic%20Bund%20in%20Shanghai.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65027387992da60019ebff15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223184%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20couple%20pose%20for%20wedding%20photos%20on%20the%20historic%20Bund%20in%20Shanghai.%3Cp%3EMark%20Rolston%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20securities%20regulator%20is%20cracking%20down%20on%20speedy%20share%20sales%20following%20divorces%20among%20the%20country's%20elite.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20least%20eight%20major%20shareholders%20of%20listed%20companies%20transferred%20stocks%20worth%20%243.9%20billion%20to%20ex-spouses%20this%20year%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20eight%20former%20couples%20announced%20plans%20to%20sell%20their%20shares%20in%20the%20months%20following%20their%20breakup.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20securities%20regulator%20is%20cracking%20down%20on%20speedy%20share%20disposals%20by%20wealthy%20couples%20after%20their%20divorces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20clampdown%20is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Finvestor.szse.cn%2Fknowledge%2Fcompany%2Fdcffv%2Ft20180118_538621.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurities%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20restricts%20company%20executives%20and%20shareholders%20who%20own%20more%20than%20a%205%25%20stake%20to%20sell%20only%202%25%20of%20the%20float%20in%20the%20market%20within%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20came%20after%20certain%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnew