%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.csrc.gov.cn%2Fcsrc%2Fc100028%2Fc7426770%2Fcontent.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epledged%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20close%20the%20loophole%20a%20month%20later.%20The%20key%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sse.com.cn%2Flawandrules%2Fguide%2Fscjgznlc%2Fc%2Fc_20230825_5725657.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShanghai%20Stock%20Exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.szse.cn%2Faboutus%2Ftrends%2Fnews%2Ft20230825_602967.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShenzhen%20Stock%20Exchange%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0then%20said%20they%20would%20still%20be%20applying%20the%20same%202%25%20share%20sale%20limits%20to%20major%20shareholders%20even%20after%20the%20divorces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20by%20China's%20securities%20came%20as%20Beijing%20is%20trying%20to%20bolster%20confidence%20in%20its%20flagging%20economy%20and%20markets%20that%20have%20been%20struggling%20to%20recover%20after%20a%20post-COVID%20spurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-economy-investors-stock-market-selloff-property-crisis-debt-deflation-2023-9%3F_gl%3D1*1o5k8jx*_ga*MTM0MjM1NDU5My4xNjg1MTUzMTcw*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5NDY1NzAxMi40NDQuMS4xNjk0NjU5MDc1LjYwLjAuMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edumped%20a%20record%20%2412%20billion%20of%20Chinese%20stock%20last%20month%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0per%20JPMorgan%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-stock-market-rescue-economy-debt-deflation-unemployment-growth-crisis-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20government%20announced%20new%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20including%20reducing%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F