amount-australia-1235723153%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala's%20New%20Nipah%20Case%20Takes%20Total%20Count%20To%205%2C%20706%20On%20Contact%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKerala%20Health%20Minister%20Veena%20George%20on%20Wednesday%20confirmed%20another%20case%20of%20the%20Nipah%20virus%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20number%20of%20infections%20in%20the%20state%20to%20five.%20A%2024-year-old%20health%20worker%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Kozhikode%20has%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20virus%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20706%20are%20on%20the%20contact%20list%2C%20of%20which%2C%2077%20are%20in%20the%20high-risk%20category%2C%20while%20153%20are%20health%20workers.%20Nobody%20in%20the%20high-risk%20category%20is%20showing%20symptoms%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2013%20people%20are%20presently%20in%20the%20hospital%20under%20observation%2C%20and%20are%20showing%20mild%20symptoms%20like%20headache.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20advised%20that%20the%20high-risk%20contacts%20should%20remain%20inside%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-scrambles-all-resources-to-save-boy-infected-with-nipah-critical-4387731%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKerala%20government%20has%20formed%2019%20core%20committees%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20coordinate%20all%20measures.%20Volunteer%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20by%20the%20local%20self%20government%20to%20help%20deliver%20necessities%20to%20those%20under%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brain-damaging%20virus%20has%20so%20far%20killed%20two%20people%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Ms%20Veena%20George%20said%20that%20the%20state%20is%20aiming%20for%20%26quot%3Bproactive%20detection%26quot%3B%20of%20infection%20before%20cases%20are%20confirmed%20in%20labs.%20The%20health%20administration%20is%20monitoring%20clinical%20symptoms%20so%20that%20alerts%20can%20be%20sounded%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20administration%2C%20Ms%20George%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fnipah-nipah-in-kerala-veena-george-as-nipah-returns-how-kerala-plans-to-prevent-its-spread-4385146%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20focusing%20on%20tracing%20contacts%20of%20infected%20persons%20early%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20isolating%20those%20with%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20in%20Assembly%20today%2C%20the%20health%20minister%20said%20seven%20village%20panchayats%20--%20Atanchery%2C%20Maruthonkara%2C%20Tiruvallur%2C%20Kuttiyadi%2C%20Kayakkodi%2C%20Villyapalli%2C%20and%20Kavilumpara%20--%20in%20Kozhikode%20district%20have%20been%20declared%20containment%20zones.%20The%20creation%20of%20containment%20zones%20is%20part%20of%20the%20state%20government's%20strategy%20to%20limit%20the%20spread%20of%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEducation%20Minister%20V%20Sivankutty%20has%20also%20directed%20Public%20Education%20Director%20to%20organize%20online%20classes%20for%20students%20of%20all%20schools%20in%20the%20containment%20zone%20so%20that%20they%20can%20attend%20classes%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Nipah%20virus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENipah%20virus%20(NiV)%20is%20a%20zoonotic%20virus%20and%20is%20transmitted%20from%20animals%20(such%20as%20bats%20or%20pigs)%20to%20humans.%C2%A0It%20can%20also%20be%20transmitted%20through%20contaminated%20food%20or%20directly%20between%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFruit%20bats%20of%20the%20Pteropodidae%20family%20are%20said%20to%20be%20the%20natural%20host%20of%20Nipah%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20Nipah%20virus%20symptoms%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20infected%20people%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fkerala-reports-two-nipah-virus-deaths-know-symptoms-transmission-preventive-measures-and-more-4384048%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENipah%20virus%20causes%20a%20range%20of%20illnesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20asymptomatic%20(subclinical)%20infection%20to%20acute%20respiratory%20illness%20and%20fatal%20encephalitis.%20The%20virus%20can%20also%20cause%20severe%20disease%20in%20animals%20such%20as%20pigs%2C%20resulting%20in%20significant%20economic%20losses%20for%20farmers.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%2C%20infected%20people%20initially%20develop%20symptoms%20including%20fever%2C%20headaches%2C%20myalgia%20(muscle%20pain)%2C%20vomiting%20and%20sore%20throat.%20This%20can%20be%20followed%20by%20dizziness%2C%20drowsiness%2C%20altered%20consciousness%2C%20and%20neurological%20signs%20that%20indicate%20acute%20encephalitis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20can%20also%20experience%20atypical%20pneumonia%20and%20severe%20respiratory%20problems%2C%20including%20acute%20respiratory%20distress.%20Encephalitis%20and%20seizures%20occur%20in%20severe%20cases%2C%20progressing%20to%20coma%20within%2024%20to%2048%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENipah%20virus%20incubation%20period%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20WHO%2C%20the%20incubation%20period%20(interval%20from%20infection%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20symptoms)%20is%20believed%20to%20range%20from%204%20to%2014%20days.%20However%2C%20an%20incubation%20period%20as%20long%20as%2045%20days%20has%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20who%20survive%20acute%20encephalitis%20make%20a%20full%20recovery%2C%20but%20long-term%20neurologic%20conditions%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20survivors.%20%C2%A0Approximately%2020%25%20of%20patients%20are%20left%20with%20residual%20neurological%20consequences%20such%20as%20seizure%20disorder%20and%20personality%20changes.%20A%20small%20number%20of%20people%20who%20recover%20subsequently%20relapse%20or%20develop%20delayed%20onset%20encephalitis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20fatality%20rate%20is%20estimated%20at%2040%25%20to%2075%25.%20This%20rate%20can%20vary%20by%20outbreak%20depending%20on%20local%20capabilities%20for%20epidemiological%20surveillance%20and%20clinical%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694661360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fnipah-virus-_625x300_1527298560973.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-another-nipah-virus-case-in-kerala-total-5-now-4387977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20Health%20Minister%20Veena%20George%20on%20Wednesday%20confirmed%20another%20case%20of%20the%20Nipah%20virus%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20number%20of%20infections%20in%20the%20state%20to%20five.%20A%2024-year-old%20health%20worker%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Kozhikode%20has%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20virus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-another-nipah-virus-case-in-kerala-total-5-now-4387977%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-another-nipah-virus-case-in-kerala-total-5-now-4387977%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-another-nipah-virus-case-in-kerala-total-5-now-4387977%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20found%20a%20massive%20lithium%20deposit%20inside%20an%20ancient%20US%20volcano%20that%20could%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20American%20clean%20energy%20but%20spell%20disaster%20for%20Native%20Americans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222933%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20general%20view%20shows%20the%20brine%20pools%20of%20Albemarle%20Chile%20lithium%20plant%20placed%20on%20the%20Atacama%20salt%20flat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501f514992da60019eba73b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20general%20view%20shows%20the%20brine%20pools%20of%20Albemarle%20Chile%20lithium%20plant%20placed%20on%20the%20Atacama%20salt%20flat.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FIvan%20Alvarado%2FFile%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EScientists%20measured%20significant%20levels%20of%20lithium%20trapped%20in%20clay%20deposits%20in%20an%20extinct%20US%20volcano.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20mostly%20relies%20on%20lithium%20imports%2C%20which%20it%20uses%20for%20rechargeable%20batteries%20in%20electric%20cars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELithium%20independence%20would%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20clean%20energy%20but%20Native%20Americans%20are%20already%20suffering%20for%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20McDermitt%20Caldera%20is%20probably%20unfamiliar.%20It%20belongs%20to%20an%20extinct%20volcano%20that%20last%20erupted%20approximately%2016%20million%20years%20ago.%20But%20for%20lithium%20hunters%2C%20it's%20the%20biggest%20gold%20mine%20find%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20scientists%20published%20a%20shocking%20discovery%20that%20the%20caldera%20contains%20what%20could%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2075-163X%2F10%2F1%2F68%5C%22%3Elargest%20amount%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20lithium%20in%20the%20world%2C%20locked%20up%20in%20an%20unusual%20type%20of%20clay%20called%20illite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20research%20has%20gone%20one%20step%20further.%20In%20August%2C%20researchers%20reported%20that%20the%20illite%20in%20the%20southern%20portion%20of%20McDermitt%20Caldera%2C%20called%20Thacker%20Pass%2C%20contains%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.adh8183%5C%22%3E1.8%25%20lithium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20almost%20double%20the%20lithium%20present%20in%20magnesium%20smectite%2C%20the%20main%20type%20of%20clay%20mined%20for%20lithium%2C%20today%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chemistryworld.com%2Fnews%2Flithium-discovery-in-us-volcano-could-be-biggest-deposit-ever-found%2F4018032.article%5C%22%3EChemistry%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20a%20couple%20of%20things%3A%20McDermitt%20Caldera%2C%20located%20along%20the%20Nevada-Oregon%20border%2C%20could%20contain%20over%20132%20million%20tons%20of%20lithium%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20to%20meet%20global%20demand%20for%20decades%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjalopnik.com%2Fa-volcano-in-the-u-s-could-contain-the-biggest-lithium-1850825799%3Futm_source%3Dflipboard%26utm_content%3Dtopic%252Fscience%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJalopnik%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20means%20the%20US%2C%20which%20only%20has%20one%20active%20lithium%20mine%2C%20may%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20other%20countries%20for%20much%20of%20its%20lithium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20an%20estimated%208%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20lithium%20embedded%20in%20its%20soil%2C%20ranking%20it%20in%20the%20top%20five%20countries%20worldwide%20with%20the%20most%20reserves%2C%20yet%20the%20country%20makes%20up%20just%201%25%20of%20global%20lithium%20production%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmineralsmakelife.org%2Fblog%2Flithium-electrifying-america%2F%5C%22%3EMinerals%20Make%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20demand%20for%20lithium%20is%20only%20expected%20to%20soar%20since%20it's%20a%20key%20ingredient%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flithium-mining-electric-vehicles-climate-crisis-2023-5%5C%22%3Erechargeable%20batteries%20used%20in%20electric%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20needs%20more%20lithium%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20supply%20chains%20for%20electric%20vehicles.%20And%20McDermitt%20Caldera%20could%20be%20that%20resource.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20change%20the%20dynamics%20of%20lithium%20globally%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20price%2C%20security%20of%20supply%2C%20and%20geopolitics%2C%26quot%3B%20Anouk%20Borst%2C%20a%20geologist%20at%20KU%20Leuven%20University%20and%20the%20Royal%20Museum%20for%20Central%20Africa%20in%20Tervuren%2C%20Belgium%2C%20told%20Chemistry%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20just%20one%20thing%3A%20local%20Indigenous%20communities%20say%20Thacker%20Pass%20is%20sacred%20land%20where%20they%20harvest%20traditional%20medicines%2C%20foods%2C%20and%20supplies%20for%20sacred%20ceremonies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2021%2Fdec%2F02%2Fthacker-pass-lithium-mine-fight-save-sacred-land-nevada%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20burial%20sites%20there.%20There's%20medicines%20and%20roots%20there%2C%20there's%20ecosystems%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20still%20life%20back%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Gary%20McKinney%20of%20the%20Shoshone-Paiute%20Indigenous%20tribe%20local%20to%20Thacker%20Pass%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F3%2F15%2Fnevada-lithium-mine-breaks-ground-despite-indigenous-opposition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20all%20being%20sacrificed%20supposedly%20to%20fix%20the%20climate%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKinney%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indigenous%20group%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeopleofredmountain.com%2Fabout-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20of%20Red%20Mountain%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20opposed%20lithium%20mining%20at%20Thacker%20Pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20federal%20court%20denied%20opponent's%20requests%20for%20an%20injunction%2C%20and%20in%20March%20the%20company%20Lithium%20Americas%20said%20workers%20had%20started%20drilling%20and%20building%20infrastructure%20at%20the%20site%2C%20Al%20Jazeera%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20needs%20to%20know%20that%20this%20lithium%20mining%2C%20and%20this%20fast-tracking%20of%20lithium%20mining%2C%20is%20a%20continuation%20of%20r