%20is%20NOT%20the%20official%20position%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20MFA%20and%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20President%20of%20Ukraine%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Ukraine%20embassy%20responded%20following%20the%20circulation%20of%20clips%20of%20Podolyak%E2%80%99s%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20surfaced%20after%20Russian%20social%20media%20users%20and%20official%20media%20outlets%20translated%20and%20circulated%20clips%20from%20an%20interview%20Podolyak%20gave%20to%20a%20YouTube%20channel.%20%E2%80%9CChina%20and%20India%20are%20not%20able%20to%20analyse%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20actions%E2%80%9A%20low%20intellectual%20potential%2C%20unfortunately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20translation%20provided%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.ru%2Fmezhdunarodnaya-panorama%2F18730491%5C%22%3ERussia%E2%80%99s%20state%20news%20agency%20%3Cem%3ETASS%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%20they%20invest%20in%20science.%20India%20has%20sent%20a%20lander%20to%20the%20Moon%2C%20but%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20say%20that%20this%20country%20understands%20what%20the%20modern%20world%20is%20about.%20The%20problem%20of%20these%20countries%2C%20India%20and%20China%2C%20is%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20analyse%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20own%20steps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20has%20been%20no%20response%20from%20India%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxwfw_665399%2Fs2510_665401%2F202309%2Ft20230913_11142374.html%5C%22%3EChinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20context%20of%20these%20remarks%20and%20will%20leave%20it%20to%20the%20speaker%20to%20offer%20explanations.%20On%20the%20Ukraine%20crisis%2C%20China%20always%20acts%20in%20a%20responsible%20manner%20to%20promote%20talks%20for%20peace%20and%20facilitate%20a%20political%20settlement.%20The%20individual%20you%20cited%20should%20view%20China%E2%80%99s%20