night%2C%20a%20series%20of%20events%20started%20to%20unfold%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20George%20Bivens%20of%20the%20Pennsylvania%20state%20police%20told%20reporters%20in%20Chester%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThank%20you%20to%20our%20law%20enforcement%20partners%20and%20the%20community%20whose%20support%20brought%20this%20operation%20to%20a%20successful%20conclusion.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FogmZKg1fGr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FogmZKg1fGr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20PA%20State%20Police%20(%40PAStatePolice)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPAStatePolice%2Fstatus%2F1701982519170642379%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EA%20burglar%20alarm%20went%20off%20within%20a%20police%20perimeter%2C%20drawing%20law%20enforcement's%20attention%2C%20and%20an%20aircraft%20picked%20up%20a%20heat%20signal%20in%20the%20woods%2C%20Bivens%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20storm%20breaking%20overhead%20the%20aircraft%20had%20to%20retreat%2C%20but%20in%20the%20morning%20police%20moved%20in%20on%20their%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20the%20element%20of%20surprise.%20Cavalcante%20did%20not%20realize%20he%20was%20surrounded%2C%26quot%3B%20Bivens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20still%20refused%20to%20surrender%20and%20instead%20tried%20to%20crawl%20away%20through%20thick%20underbrush%20while%20still%20clutching%20a%20stolen%20rifle%2C%20Bivens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%20law%20enforcement%20released%20their%20K9%20unit%20which%20%26quot%3Bsubdued%20him%20and%20team%20members...%20moved%20in.%20He%20continued%20to%20resist%20but%20was%20forcibly%20taken%20into%20custody%2C%26quot%3B%20Bivens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20eyewitness%20described%20the%20surge%20of%20energy%20as%20police%20closed%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20basically%20just%20saw%20them%20storming%2C%20checking%20the%20tree%20lines%2C%20checking%20the%20stream%20and%20out%20of%20nowhere%20everybody%20started%20to%20congregate%20back%20by%20the%20shed%20and%20here%20they%20were%20already%20bringing%20him%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20store%20manager%20Jim%20Martin%20told%20NBC%20Philadelphia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFootage%20on%20CNN%20showed%20heavily%20armed%20officers%20in%20camouflage%20handcuffing%20the%20Brazilian%20national%20and%20removing%20his%20shirt%2C%20revealing%20a%20large%20tattoo%20on%20his%20back%2C%20before%20placing%20him%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20police%20vehicle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECavalcante%2C%20who%20had%20been%20convicted%20of%20murdering%20his%20girlfriend%20--%20stabbing%20her%20dozens%20of%20times%20in%20front%20of%20her%20children%20--%20had%20just%20begun%20his%20sentence%20on%20August%2031%20when%20he%20climbed%20over%20the%20prison%20wall%20and%20cleared%20two%20razor-wire%20fences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeasuring%20just%20five%20feet%20(1.52%20meters)%20tall%2C%20Cavalcante%20had%20raised%20the%20stakes%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20entering%20a%20private%20garage%20to%20steal%20a%20.22%20caliber%20rifle%20with%20a%20scope%20--%20then%20dodging%20pistol%20gunfire%20from%20the%20pursuing%20homeowner%20to%20get%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20declared%20him%20%26quot%3Barmed%20and%20extremely%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChester%20County%20District%20Attorney%20Deb%20Ryan%20told%20reporters%20one%20of%20the%20first%20calls%20made%20after%20Cavalcante's%20capture%20was%20to%20his%20victim's%20family%2C%20%26quot%3Bwho%20as%20you%20can%20imagine%20have%20been%20living%20in%20a%20complete%20nightmare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20now%20finally%20sleep%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20long%20struggled%20to%20narrow%20down%20the%20fugitive's%20location%20in%20the%20heavily%20wooded%20area.%20However%2C%20Cavalcante%20repeatedly%20popped%20up%20on%20private%20