ters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20rain%20interruption%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%2047th%20over%20of%20India's%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20into%20the%20technicalities%2C%20Gambhir%20explained%20why%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20play%20certain%20deliveries%20on%20the%20backfoot%20and%20not%20the%20front%20foot%20in%20order%20to%20be%20effective%20in%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20batsman%20we%20often%20try%20to%20play%20the%20angle%2C%20but%20if%20the%20ball%20spins%20from%20there%20then%20things%20become%20difficult.%20If%20you%20deliver%20it%20closer%20to%20the%20wicket%20then%20it%20becomes%20easier%2C%20but%20when%20you%20deliver%20it%20wider%20from%20the%20crease%20then%20it%20becomes%20difficult.%20And%20that%20is%20why%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20play%20it%20off%20the%20backfoot%20rather%20than%20frontfoot%2C%20where%20both%20the%20edges%20are%20tested.%20Look%20at%20Hardik's%20dismissal.%20And%20you%20mentioned%20(Ajantha)%20Mendis...he%20had%20carrom%20ball%20and%20we%20did%20not%20even%20know%20how%20those%20deliveries%20would%20behave.%20But%20these%20were%20proper%20left-arm%20spin%20deliveries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGill%20could%20have%20defended%20that%20ball.%20You%20cannot%20say%20that%20it%20was%20an%20unplayable%20delivery.%20Look%20at%20the%20bat%20face%2C%20it%20is%20towards%20the%20leg%20side...%20towards%20mid-on.%20Against%20such%20deliveries%2C%20you%20should%20always%20play%20it%20towards%20mid-off%20or%20towards%20the%20bowler.%20The%20moment%20you%20go%20for%20mid-on%20you%20are%20giving%20the%20chance%20for%20an%20outside%20edge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694657880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fifltfvrg_gambhir-_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fgautam-gambhir-refuses-to-spare-rohit-kohli-rahul-gill-after-indias-top-ord