agle%20can%20be%20flying%20and%20suddenly%20get%20dive-bombed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20crows%20out%20of%20nowhere.%20Even%20though%20the%20eagle%20is%20not%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20the%20crows%2C%20it%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20their%20chicks%20and%20eggs%2C%20so%20it's%20in%20their%20best%20interest%20to%20force%20the%20eagle%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20orcas%20and%20humpbacks%2C%20it%20may%20also%20be%20the%20seal%20that's%20forcing%20the%20close%20encounter.%20While%20most%20people%20believe%20the%20humpbacks%20are%20swimming%20over%20to%20save%20the%20seal%2C%20the%20seal%20may%20actually%20be%20swimming%20toward%20the%20humpbacks%20to%20save%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrites%20explained%20that%20in%20British%20Columbia%20there%20are%20many%20occasions%20where%20sea%20lions%20come%20under%20attack%20by%20killer%20whales%20and%20find%20something%20really%20big%20to%20take%20refuge%20behind%20%E2%80%94%20including%20bigger%20whales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20people%20interpret%20it%20as%2C%20'Oh%2C%20the%20whales%20came%20to%20save%20the%20sea%20lions.'%20I%20hear%20that%20over%20and%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20I%20see%20is%20a%20relatively%20small%2C%20defenseless%20creature%20trying%20to%20get%20away%2C%20so%20that%20can%20be%20getting%20in%20and%20around%20humpback%20whales%2C%20or%20can%20be%20getting%20in%20or%20around%20someone's%20boat%2C%20which%20often%20happens%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DesjW906LnKo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESea%20lions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBT5f1YXWeVU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseals%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20captured%20hopping%20onto%20boats%20in%20order%20to%20evade%20killer%20whales.%20Footage%20captured%20last%20year%20off%20the%20UK's%20Shetland%20Islands%20showed%20a%20clever%20seal%20appearing%20to%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3