i-killing-web-grand-bargain-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edo%20what%20they%20can%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stop%20their%20data%20from%20being%20scraped%20and%20saved%20to%20expand%20datasets%20needed%20to%20train%20AI%20models.%20However%2C%20Instacart%20also%20added%20language%20that%20left%20it%20a%20window%20to%20do%20just%20that%20with%20its%20own%20customers'%20data%2C%20saying%20its%20license%20now%20allows%20it%20to%20%26quot%3B...otherwise%20enhance%20our%20machine%20learning%20algorithms%2C%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20operating%2C%20providing%2C%20and%20improving%20the%20services.%26quot%3B%20That%20language%20was%20not%20in%20its%20previous%20terms%2C%20according%20to%20a%20version%20seen%20through%20the%20Internet%20Archive.%20Instacart%20also%20did%20not%20specify%20these%20changes%20in%20its%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Instacart%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20is%20preparing%20to%20deploy%20some%20sort%20of%20AI%20tool%20on%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20incorporating%20generative-AI%20experiences%20into%20our%20products%20to%20assist%20with%20customers'%20grocery%20shopping%20questions%20and%20help%20them%20make%20food-related%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20updated%20terms%20clarify%20that%20generative%20AI%20is%20now%20a%20part%20of%20Instacart's%20offering%20subject%20to%20restrictions%20on%20misuse%20and%20the%20other%20general%20provisions%20of%20our%20terms%2C%20and%20the%20standards%20for%20those%20features%20remain%20the%20same%20as%20our%20entire%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20companies%20do%20disclose%20what%20they've%20changed%20in%20an%20update%20to%20a%20Terms%20agreement%20or%20Privacy%20Policy%20that%20covers%20the%20use%20of%20data%20for%20AI%2C%20they're%20often%20vague.%20Microsoft's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D6e743eec844a69632595c59f751cb5b4f7faadc396665c7cf5ae40c719341f28%26postID%