20about%26quot%3B%20what%20they%20say%20in%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20best%20practice%2C%20don't%20include%20any%20personal%20information%2C%20like%20your%20home%20address%20or%20phone%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Meta%20advises.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20August%2C%20it%20created%20a%20simple%20form%20where%20users%20could%20%26quot%3Brequest%26quot%3B%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20their%20data%20being%20used%20to%20train%20AI%20models.%20The%20company%20does%20not%20say%20whether%20it%20will%20abide%20by%20any%20such%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20tech%20employee%20or%20someone%20else%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Kali%20Hays%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akhays%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekhays%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20on%20secure%20messaging%20app%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.org%2Fdownload%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ESignal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20at%20949-280-0267%2C%20or%20through%20Twitter%20DM%20at%20%40hayskali.%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20non-work%20device.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-updated-terms-to-use-customer-data-to-train-ai-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694641665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64faebe83d3923001976834b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-updated-terms-to-use-customer-data-to-train-ai-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20companies%20are%20quietly%20giving%20themselves%20permission%20to%20use%20consumer%20data%20to%20train%20generative%20AI%20models%20and%20tools.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kali%20Hays)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-updated-terms-to