0smoke%20their%20caregivers'%20marijuana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20starred%20Mila%20Kunis%2C%20Ashton%20Kutcher%2C%20Jane%20Fonda%2C%20Chris%20Rock%2C%20and%20even%20included%20Ethereum%20founder%20Vitalik%20Buterin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20holders%20of%20the%20NFT%20are%20able%20to%20view%20the%20series.%20None%20of%20the%20celebrities%20that%20starred%20in%20the%20show%20were%20involved%20with%20the%20SEC%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20SEC%2C%20Stoner%20Cats%20NFTs%20were%20marketed%20to%20the%20public%20with%20enough%20specific%20benefits%20that%20alluded%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20you%20could%20potentially%20make%20a%20profit%20from%20buying%20them%20and%20re-selling%20them%20in%20the%20secondary%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20the%20marketing%20campaign%2C%20the%20SC2%20team%20emphasized%20its%20expertise%20as%20Hollywood%20producers%2C%20its%20knowledge%20of%20crypto%20projects%2C%20and%20the%20well-known%20actors%20involved%20in%20the%20web%20series%2C%20leading%20investors%20to%20expect%20profits%20because%20a%20successful%20web%20series%20could%20cause%20the%20resale%20value%20of%20the%20Stoner%20Cats%20NFTs%20in%20the%20secondary%20market%20to%20rise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SEC%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20violated%20the%20Securities%20Act%20of%201933%2C%20as%20the%20NFTs%20were%20not%20registered%20as%20a%20security%20before%20their%20sale%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegistration%20of%20securities%2C%20including%20crypto%20asset%20securities%2C%20protects%20investors%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20disclosures%20so%20they%20can%20make%20informed%20investing%20decisions.%20Stoner%20Cats%20wanted%20all%20the%20benefits%20of%20offering%20and%20selling%20a%20security%20to%20the%20public%20but%20ignored%20the%20legal%20responsibilities%20that%20come%20with%20doing%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20SEC%20associate%20director%20Carolyn%20Welshhans%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20peak%20in%20August%202021%2C%20one%20Stoner%20Cat%20NFT%20sold%20for%20931%20ether%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20OpenSea.%20Based%20on%20ether%20prices%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20Stoner%20Cat%20NFT%20was%20worth%20nearly%20%243%20million.%20Today%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20a%20Stoner%20Cat%20NFT%20for%20about%20.045%20ether%2C%20or%20%2480%2C%20representing%20a%2099.99%25%20decline%20from%20its%20peak.%20But%20for%20most%20Stoner%20Cat%20NFTs%2C%20they%20never%20eclipsed%20their%20initial%20offering%20price%20of%20%24800.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SEC%20also%20ordered%20Stoner%20Cats%202%2C%20LLC%20to%20destroy%20all%20of%20the%20NFTs%20it%20currently%20holds%20and%20issue%20a%20notice%20of%20the%20violation%20across%20its%20website%20and%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstoner-cats-nft-sec-securities-violation-ashton-kutcher-mila-kunis-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694634613000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650207541afe8f0019e9d1a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fstoner-cats-nft-sec-securities-violation-ashton-kutcher-mila-kunis-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20its%20peak%20in%20August%202021%2C%20one%20Stoner%20Cat%20NFT%20sold%20for%20931%20ether%2C%20or%20about%20%243%20million.%20Today%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20a%20Stoner%20Cat%20NFT%20for%20about%20%2480.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A155%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fstoner-cats-nft-sec-securities-violation-ashton-kutcher-mila-kunis-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Odetari%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20EDM%20Star%20Who%20Went%20From%20Substitute%20Teacher%20to%20Chart%20Topper%22%2C%22conte