%20Meets%20Radiation%20Rules%2C%20Disputes%20French%20Findings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20defended%20its%20iPhone%2012%20model%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20a%20French%20watchdog%20ordered%20a%20halt%20to%20its%20sales%20citing%20breaches%20of%20European%20Union%20radiation%20exposure%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20move%20raised%20the%20prospect%20of%20further%20bans%20in%20Europe.%20Germany's%20network%20regulator%20BNetzA%20said%20it%20might%20launch%20similar%20proceedings%20and%20was%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20French%20authorities%2C%20while%20Spain's%20OCU%20consumers'%20group%20urged%20authorities%20there%20to%20halt%20the%20sales%20of%20the%20iPhone%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20the%20iPhone%2012%2C%20launched%20in%202020%2C%20was%20certified%20by%20multiple%20international%20bodies%20as%20compliant%20with%20global%20radiation%20standards%2C%20that%20it%20had%20provided%20several%20Apple%20and%20third-party%20lab%20results%20proving%20the%20phone's%20compliance%20to%20the%20French%20agency%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20contesting%20its%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20have%20conducted%20a%20vast%20number%20of%20studies%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20to%20assess%20health%20risks%20resulting%20from%20mobile%20phones.%20According%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%2C%20no%20adverse%20health%20effects%20have%20so%20far%20been%20established%20as%20being%20caused%20by%20mobile%20phone%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrance's%20Agence%20Nationale%20des%20Fr%C3%A9quences%20(ANFR)%20told%20Apple%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20halt%20iPhone12%20sales%20in%20France%20after%20tests%20that%20it%20said%20showed%20the%20phone's%20Specific%20Absorption%20Rate%20(SAR)-%20a%20gauge%20of%20the%20rate%20of%20radiofrequency%20energy%20absorbed%20by%20the%20body%20from%20a%20piece%20of%20equipment%20-%20was%20higher%20than%20legally%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watchdog%20said%20it%20would%20send%20agents%20to%20Apple%20stores%20and%20other%20distributors%20to%20check%20the%20model%20was%20no%20longer%20being%20sold%20and%20a%20failure%20to%20act%20would%20result%20in%20the%20recall%20of%20iPhone%2012s%20already%20sold%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20experts%20said%20there%20were%20no%20safety%20risks%20as%20regulatory%20limits%20on%20SAR%20were%20set%20well%20below%20levels%20where%20scientists%20have%20found%20evidence%20of%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20health%20and%20safety%20point%20of%20view%2C%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20this%20is%20putting%20anyone%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Rodney%20Croft%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20International%20Commission%20on%20Non-Ionizing%20Radiation%20Protection%20(ICNIRP)%2C%20which%20sets%20global%20guidelines%20on%20the%20SAR%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20limits%20-%20based%20on%20the%20risk%20of%20burns%20or%20heatstroke%20from%20the%20phone's%20radiation%20-%20are%20already%20set%20ten%20times%20below%20the%20level%20where%20scientists%20found%20evidence%20of%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECroft%20said%20the%20French%20findings%20could%20differ%20from%20those%20recorded%20by%20other%20regulators%20because%20ANFR%20assesses%20radiation%20with%20a%20method%20that%20assumes%20direct%20skin%20contact%2C%20without%20intermediate%20textile%20layers%2C%20between%20the%20device%20and%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20French%20government%20source%20also%20said%20the%20French%20test%20was%20different%20from%20the%20method%20used%20by%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmartphone%20radiation%20tests%20have%20so%20far%20led%20to%2042%20sales%20stops%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20the%20first%20time%20Apple%20has%20been%20affected%20by%20such%20a%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecall%20Threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ANFR%20said%20accredited%20labs%20had%20found%20absorption%20of%20electromagnetic%20energy%20by%20the%20body%20at%205.74%20watts%20per%20kilogram%20during%20tests%20simulating%20when%20the%20iPhone%2012%20was%20being%20held%20in%20the%20hand%20or%20kept%20in%20a%20trouser%20pocket.%20The%20European%20standard%20is%20a%20specific%20absorption%20rate%20of%204.0%20watts%20per%20kilogram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EANFR%20added%20the%20tests%20showed%20the%20phone%20complied%20with%20so-called%20body-SAR%20standards%20when%20it%20was%20in%20a%20jacket%20pocket%20or%20bag.%20It%20also%20passed%20the%20French%20tests%20when%20held%20directly%20to%20the%20head%20as%20if%20making%20a%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrance's%20junior%20minister%20for%20the%20digital%20economy%2C%20Jean-Noel%20Barrot%2C%20said%20a%20software%20update%20would%20be%20sufficient%20to%20fix%20the%20radiation%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple%20is%20expected%20to%20respond%20within%20two%20weeks%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20told%20daily%20Le%20Parisien%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20fail%20to%20do%20so%2C%20I%20am%20prepared%20to%20order%20a%20recall%20of%20all%20iPhones%2012%20in%20circulation.%20The%20rule%20is%20the%20same%20for%20everyone%2C%20including%20the%20digital%20giants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EANFR%20will%20now%20pass%20on%20its%20findings%20to%20regulators%20in%20other%20European%20Union%20member%20states.%20%26quot%3BIn%20practical%20terms%2C%20this%20decision%20could%20have%20a%20snowball%20effect%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Barrot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20procedure%20in%20France%20has%20a%20guiding%20function%20for%20Europe%20as%20a%20whole%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Germany's%20BNetzA%20network%20regulator%2C%20adding%20it%20might%20launch%20similar%20proceedings%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGermany's%20radiation%20watchdog%20BfS%20also%20said%20the%20French%20decision%20could%20have%20implications%20for%20all%20of%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20doesn't%20break%20out%20its%20sales%20by%20country%20or%20model.%20Its%20revenues%20totalled%20about%20%2495%20billion%20in%20Europe%20last%20year%2C%20making%20the%20region%20its%20second%20biggest%20behind%20the%20Americas.%20Some%20estimates%20say%20it%20sold%20over%2050%20million%20iPhones%20last%20year%20in%20Europe.%20The%20company%20launched%20the%20iPhone%2015%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer%2C%20which%20sets%20global%20guidelines%20on%20SAR%20limits%2C%20classed%20the%20radiofrequency%20electromagnetic%20fields%20resulting%20from%20mobile%20phone%20use%20as%20%26quot%3Bpossibly%20carcinogenic%26quot%3B%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20designation%20-%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20sweetener%20aspartame%2C%20aloe%20vera%20extract%20and%20some%20pickled%20vegetables%20-%20flags%20there%20is%20limited%20evidence%20of%20something%20potentially%20causing%20cancer%2C%20and%20is%20also%20intended%20to%20motivate%20more%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694630880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-02%2Fapple-generic-afp_650x400_41456246344.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-says-iphone-12-meets-radiation-rules-disputes-french-findings-4387799%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20defended%20its%20iPhone%2012%20model%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20a%20French%20watchdog%20ordered%20a%20halt%20to%20its%20sales%20citing%20breaches%20of%20European%20Union%20radiation%20exposure%20limits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-says-iphone-12-meets-radiation-rules-disputes-french-findings-4387799%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-says-iphone-12-meets-radiation-rules-disputes-french-findings-4387799%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-s