involved%20in%20this%20tragic%20case.%20The%20Consulate%20%26amp%3B%20Embassy%20will%20continue%20to%20closely%20follow%20up%20on%20this%20matter%20with%20all%20concerned%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Indian%20diplomatic%20mission.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspdblotter.seattle.gov%2F2023%2F01%2F30%2Fchief-diazs-statement-regarding-fatal-collision%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Kandula%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20police%20officer%20Kevin%20Dave%20who%20was%20on%20way%20to%20attend%20a%20call.%20Another%20police%20officer%2C%20Daniel%20Auderer%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Officers%20Guild%2C%20was%20assigned%20to%20check%20whether%20Dave%20was%20under%20any%20influence.%20As%20he%20inadvertently%20left%20his%20body%20camera%20on%2C%20it%20recorded%20a%20call%20made%20to%20the%20guild%20president%20Mike%20Solan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20audio%2C%20Auderer%20laughed%20and%20said%20Kandula%E2%80%99s%20life%20had%20%E2%80%9Climited%20value%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20city%20should%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20write%20a%20check%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CEleven%20thousand%20dollars.%20She%20was%2026%20anyway%2C%E2%80%9D%20Auderer%20said%20misquoting%20her%20age%20and%20added%20%E2%80%9Cshe%20had%20limited%20value%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2023-year-old%20student%20was%20going%20to%20graduate%20this%20year%20with%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20information%20systems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20uncle%2C%20Ashok%20Mandula%20told%20the%20media%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfamily%20has%20nothing%20to%20say%E2%80%9D%20after%20reports%20over%20the%20body%20camera%20audio.%20%E2%80%9CExcept%20I%20wonder%20if%20these%20men%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20or%20granddaughters%20have%20value.%20A%20life%20is%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKandula%20was%20set%20to%20graduate%20this%20coming%20December%20with%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20information%20systems%20from%20the%20Seattle%20campus%20of%20Northeastern%20University.%20Her%20family%20said%20she%20was%20working%20toward%20supporting%20her%20mother%20in%20India.%20Instead%2C%20her%20uncle%2C%20Ashok%20Mandula%2C%20of%20Houston%2C%20had%20to%20make%20arrangements%20to%20send%20her%20body%20to%20her%20mother.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20conservative%20talk%20show%20host%20said%20that%20he%20obtained%20a%20statement%20from%20Auderer%20that%20his%20remarks%20would%20sound%20bad%20if%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Seattle%20chief%20Adrian%20Diaz%20said%20that%20the%20department%20learnt%20of%20the%20conversation%20from%20an%20employee%20who%20overheard%20it%20during%20%E2%80%9Croutine%20course%20of%20business%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Department%20contacted%20the%20Office%20of%20Police%20Accountability%20in%20early%20August%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20doing%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694629427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13235147%2FCopy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Lead-image-size-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findian-consulate-intervenes-after-reports-of-seattle-police-downplaying-death-of-indian-student%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20consulate%20said%20that%20the%20media%20reports%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Chandling%E2%80%9D%20of%20Kandula%E2%80%99s%20death%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20troubling%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findian-consulate-intervenes-after-reports-of-seattle-police-downplaying-death-of-indian-student%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former