er%20to%20collect%20her%20pension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20man's%20lawyer%20told%20local%20paper%20%3Cem%3ENya%20Wermlands-Tidningen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20buried%20at%20a%20public%20cemetery%20but%20at%20the%20farm%2C%20actually.%20So%20he%20put%20her%20in%20the%20freezer%20to%20later%20bury%20her%20outside%20and%20then%20it%20fell%20by%20the%20wayside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20allegedly%20told%20his%20friends%20and%20family%20that%20his%2060-year-old%20was%20alive%20even%20after%20she%20died%20from%20cancer%20in%202018.%20According%20to%20an%20English-language%20Norwegian%20news%20site%2C%20the%20woman's%20family%20reported%20her%20missing%20after%20losing%20contact%20with%20her%2C%20but%20the%20man%20kept%20telling%20them%20that%20she%20was%20either%20sleeping%20or%20unavailable%20before%20eventually%20telling%20them%20she%20no%20longer%20wanted%20to%20speak%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20found%20her%20body%20in%20March%20following%20a%20tip%2C%20and%20the%20man%20admitted%20that%20he%20hid%20her%20death%20and%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20told%20investigators%20that%20he%20put%20his%20wife%20in%20a%20freezer%20after%20finding%20her%20dead%20in%20their%20home.%20The%20couple%20lived%20in%20Arjang%2C%20which%20is%20about%20340%20kilometres%20west%20of%20Stockholm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20few%20local%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20man%20had%20stored%20the%20body%20in%20the%20freezer%20which%20he%20also%20used%20to%20store%20food.%C2%A0In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20man%20kept%20claiming%20the%20woman's%20pension%20and%20tax%20rebates%2C%20a%20total%20sum%20of%20more%20than%201.2%20million%20Norwegian%20kroner%20(%24116%2C000).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20man%20also%20used%20the%20freezer%20for%20other%20purposes%20which%20I%20argue%20means%20that%20the%20deceased%20person's%20sanctity%20of%20the%20grave%20was%20violated%20every%20time%20the%20man%20opened%20and%20closed%20the%20freezer%2C%20which%20is%20an%20aggravating%20circumstance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20prosecutor%20Linda%20Karlsson%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20convicted%20the%20man%20on%20charges%20of%20gross%20breach%20of%20civil%20liberties%2C%20gross%20fraud%2C%20mutilating%20a%20corpse%2C%20and%20falsification%20of%20documents%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694628360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fnvs9pie_freezer-generic-getty_625x300_14_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhusband-puts-wifes-body-in-freezer-to-collect-pension-gets-3-5-years-in-prison-4387730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20had%20preserved%20his%20wife's%20body%20in%20a%20freezer%20for%20almost%20five%20years%20in%20order%20to%20collect%20her%20pension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhusband-puts-wifes-body-in-freezer-to-collect-pension-gets-3-5-years-in-prison-4387730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhusband-puts-wifes-body-in-freezer-to-collect-pension-gets-3-5-years-in-prison-4387730%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhusband-puts-wifes-body-in-freezer-to-collect-pension-gets-3-5-years-in-prison-4387730%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WhatsApp%20Rolls%20Out%20Telegram-Like%20Channels%20Feature%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhatsApp%20has%20rolled%20out%20its%20long-awaited%20feature%2C%20WhatsApp%20Channels%2C%20in%20India%20and%20across%20more%20than%20150%20countries%2C%20marking%20an%20innovative%20development%20in%20the%20services%20provided%20by%20the%20messaging%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20parent%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2Fwhatsapp-channels-heres-everything-you-need-to-know%2F%5C%2