day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nationality%20of%20the%20dead%20woman%2C%20aged%2032%2C%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20determined%2C%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20case%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20at%20the%20Pellegrin%20hospital%20in%20Bordeaux%2C%20Benjamin%20Clouzeau%2C%20said%2012%20more%20people%20were%20still%20receiving%20emergency%20treatment%20early%20Wednesday.%20Five%20of%20them%20were%20on%20respiratory%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20included%20American%2C%20Irish%20and%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20German%20national%20travelled%20home%20for%20treatment%2C%20as%20did%20a%20resident%20of%20Barcelona%2C%20Spain%2C%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20had%20eaten%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BTchin%20Tchin%20Wine%20Bar%26quot%3B%20in%20Bordeaux%2C%20between%20September%204%20and%2010%20when%20there%20are%20typically%20large%20numbers%20of%20tourists%20in%20the%20town%2C%20famous%20for%20its%20wine%20and%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20all%20ate%20sardines%20that%20had%20been%20stored%20by%20the%20restaurant%20owner%20himself%20in%20jars%2C%20the%20DGS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBotulism%20is%20deadly%20in%20five%20to%2010%20percent%20of%20cases%20because%20of%20a%20toxin%20generated%20by%20clostridium%20botulinum%20bacteria%20that%20can%20appear%20when%20preserved%20food%20is%20insufficiently%20sterilised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20were%20still%20running%20tests%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20the%20DGS%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20could%20not%20rule%20out%20the%20emergence%20of%20further%20cases%20of%20botulism%20which%20has%20an%20incubation%20period%20of%20up%20to%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20cause%20muscle%20paralysis%20lasting%20several%20weeks%2C%20with%20the%20most%20immediate%20danger%20stemming%20from%20affected%20respiratory%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20newspaper%20Sud-Ouest%20quoted%20the%20restaurant%20owner%20as%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20thrown%20out%20some%20of%20the%20jars%20containing%20sardines%20because%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20smell%26quot%3B%20emanating%20from%20the%20containers%20when%20he%20opened%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20%26quot%3Bappeared%20in%20good%20condition%20and%20were%20served%20up%20to%20customers%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694627580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fsardines_650x400_71514199630.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-dies-of-rare-disease-after-eating-sardines-in-popular-french-town-4387687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20died%20in%20France%20from%20botulism%20after%20eating%20sardines%20at%20a%20restaurant%20last%20week%20and%2012%20other%20people%20were%20in%20treatment%20for%20the%20rare%20condition%2C%20health%20officials%20said%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-dies-of-rare-disease-after-eating-sardines-in-popular-french-town-4387687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-dies-of-rare-disease-after-eating-sardines-in-popular-french-town-4387687%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-dies-of-rare-disease-after-eating-sardines-in-popular-french-town-4387687%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20alliance%20to%20Boycott%20TV%20Shows%20That%20%E2%80%98Conduct%20Inflammatory%20Debates%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20its%20first%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20list%20of%20news%20anchors%20whose%20shows%20will%20be%20boycotted%20by%20the%20member%20parties.%20Ever%20since%20the%20alliance%20took%20shape%2C%20the%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20about%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%20hostility%E2%80%9D%20faced%20by%20opposition%20parties%20during%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime.%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20indicated%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai%20meetings%20that%20a%20strategy%20to%20counter%20propagandist%20media%20will%20be%20discussed%20among%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20coordination%20committee%2C%20thus%2C%20authorised%20the%20media%20sub-committee%20formed%20after%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%20to%20name%20and%20boycott%20television%20anchors%20who%20have%20been%20allegedly%20hostile%20to%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20all%20the%2012%20parties%20which%20participated%20in%20the%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%20K.C.%20Venugopal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coordination%20committee%20authorised%20the%20sub-group%20of%20media%20to%20decide%20upon%20the%20names%20of%20anchors%20on%20whose%20shows%20none%20of%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20will%20send%20their%20representations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChaddha%20also%20said%20that%20a%20recommendation%20in%20this%20regard%20had%20come%20from%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20media%20sub-group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20recommendation%20from%20our%20media%20sub%20group%20that%20there%20are%20certain%20anchors%20who%20conduct%20inflammatory%20debates%20in%20the%20country%2C%20so%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20put%20out%20a%20notification%20and%20stop%20going%20to%20such%20shows%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20round%20of%20seat-sharing%20discussions%2C%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20complex%20and%20heated%2C%20was%20also%20held%20at%20the%20meeting.%20Venugopal%C2%A0said%20that%20seat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%2026%20parties%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20be%20finalised%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20earliest%E2%80%9D.%20Importantly%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20alliance%20will%20take%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20country%2C%20in%20what%20is%20a%20likely%20hint%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20consensus%20between%20all%20the%20INDIA%20constituents%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20census%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20census%20was%20conspicuously%20absent%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-election-lok-sabha-together-four-committees%5C%22%3Epolitical%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20reports%20had%20hinted%20at%20the%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20(TMC%E2%80%99s)%20indecisiveness%20about%20the%20issue%20as%20the%20primary%20reason%20the%20caste%20census%20was%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20political%20resolution.%20The%20Congress%20and%20most%20other%20regional%20parties%2C%20especially%20the%20socialist%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)(JDU)%2C%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20have%20already%20been%20campaigning%20in%20favour%20of%20conducting%20a%20pan-India%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-election-lok-sabha-together-four-committees%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ready%20to%20Face%20Raids%E2%80%99%3A%20INDIA%20Parties%20Resolve%20to%20Fight%20Polls%20Together%2C%20Announce%204%20Committees%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20INDIA%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-indias-mumbai-meet-seat-sharing-to-take-back-seat-as-focus-is-on-common-programme-vision%5C%22%3EBihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20had%20said%20that%20its%20state-level%20caste%20census%20has%20already%20been%20completed%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20final%20report%20should%20come%20out%20soon.%20Other%20opposition%20parties%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20fray%20in%20demanding%20a%20caste%20census%20%E2%80%93%20an%20issue%20that%20can%20become%20an%20Achilles%E2%80%99%20heel%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20has%20remained%20indecisive%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20all%20INDIA%20parties%20are%20on%20board%20with%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20Venugopal%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20representatives%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20are%20present%20here%20decided%20these%20things%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20talk%20to%20others%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Misuse%20of%20investigative%20agencies%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wednesday%20(September%2013)%20meeting%20was%20held%20at%20NCP%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20saw%20twelve%20representatives%20of%20the%2026%20party-alliance%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20included-Sharad%20Pawar%20(NCP)%2C%20KC%20Venugopal%20(Congress)%2C%20TR%20Balu%20(DMK)%2C%20Tejasvi%20Yadav%20(RJD)%2C%20Sanjay%20Raut%20(Shiv%20Sena-Uddhav%20Thackeray)%2C%20Sanjay%20Jha%20(JDU)%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20(JMM)%2C%20Raghav%20Chaddha%20(AAP)%2C%20D%20Raja%20(CPI)%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20(National%20Conference)%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20(PDP)%2C%20and%20Javed%20Ali%20(Samajwadi%20Party).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20could%20not%20attend%20the%20meeting%20as%20he%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenugopal%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20highlighting%20the%20absence%20of%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20to%20advance%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20criticism%20of%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20investigation%20agencies%20against%20opposition%20leaders.%20%E2%80%9CShree%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20could%20not%20attend%20the%20meeting%20because%20he%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20ED%20%E2%80%93%20arising%20out%20of%20the%20vendetta%20politics%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20appeared%20before%20the%20ED%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20probe%20agency%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20into%20the%20school%20jobs%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20party%20shared%20a%20photo%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%3F%C2%A0THEY%20are%20scarED.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20truth%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETHEY%20are%20scarED.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6BsxmQQXh2%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6BsxmQQXh2%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(%40AITCofficial)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAITCofficial%2Fstatus%2F1701852604240998434%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%20the%20party%20said%20that%20Banerjee%20will%20not%20be%20%E2%80%9Ccowed%20down%20by%20the%20oppressive%20forces%E2%80%99%20intimidation%20tactics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20joint%20rally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20later%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20he%20had%20highlighted%20that%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20where%20INDIA%20parties%20are%20not%20seat%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20I%20had%20proposed%20and%20something%20that%20we%20will%20