0will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20create%20their%20own%20Channels%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhatsApp%20Channels%20are%20rolling%20out%20globally%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%20Over%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20also%20make%20it%20possible%20for%20anyone%20to%20create%20a%20channel%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20WhatsApp%20spokesperson%20said%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Meta%2C%20Channels%20aims%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprivate%20broadcast%20service.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChannels%20are%20separate%20from%20chats%20and%20who%20users%20choose%20to%20follow%20will%20not%20be%20visible%20to%20other%20followers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMeta%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20information%20of%20both%20admins%20and%20followers%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20collaboration%2C%20BCCI%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20Cricket%20team%20is%20thrilled%20to%20partner%20with%20WhatsApp%20on%20the%20launch%20of%20Channels.%20We%20kick-off%20our%20partnership%20with%20WhatsApp%20with%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20which%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20in%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3EQuestions%20Over%20Financing%20of%20Union%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Interviews%20With%20YouTube%20Influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20leverage%20Channels%20to%20generate%20excitement%20and%20support%20as%20India%20gets%20ready%20to%20host%20the%20marquee%20event%20after%20a%20decade-long%20wait.%20With%20WhatsApp%20Channels%2C%20fans%20will%20be%20aware%20of%20important%20and%20accurate%20information%20and%20news%20around%20match%20schedules%2C%20timings%2C%20scorecards%20etc.%20Get%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels%20and%20never%20miss%20out%20on%20updates%20from%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActor%20and%20entrepreneur%20Kaif%20said%20that%20Channels%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20personalised%20newsletter.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhatsApp%20Channels%20serves%20as%20a%20personalised%20newsletter%20through%20which%20I%20can%20share%20insights%20and%20updates%20with%20my%20dedicated%20audience%2C%20fans%2C%20and%20all%20those%20who%20have%20consistently%20shown%20their%20support%20throughout%20my%20journey.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhatsApp%E2%80%99s%20market%20in%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20probably%20its%20largest%20markets%20in%20the%20world%2C%20India%20is%20crucial%20for%20its%20commercial%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20then%20Union%20minister%20for%20information%20and%20technology%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimesNow%2Fstatus%2F1364857924254801921%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatsApp%20has%2053%20crore%20(530%20million)%20users%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20India%20head%20Sandhya%20Devanathan%20had%20highlighted%20that%20India%20is%20%E2%80%9Chuge%20priority%20market%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20huge%20priority%20market%20for%20the%20company.%20So%2C%20India%20has%20one%20of%20our%20largest%20user%20bases%2C%20be%20it%20on%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp.%20But%20equally%2C%20India%20is%20also%20the%20place%20where%20we%20test%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20we%20roll%20out%20globally%20as%20well.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20where%20we%20develop%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20innovative%20products%20and%20that%20investment%20will%20continue%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-a-priority-market-with-limitless-possibilities-says-meta-india-head-2673436%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPress%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98India%3A%20the%20WhatsApp%20election%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20who%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthought%20leaders%E2%80%9D%20allowed%20to%20create%20Channels%20are%2C%20at%20present%2C%20if%20that%20includes%20political%20leaders.%20Its%20likely%20impact%20in%20an%20election%20year%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20anybody%2C%20making%20it%20something%20of%20interest%20to%20political%20watchers%20and%20something%20beyond%20pure%20entertainment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%205%2C%202019%2C%20even%20before%20the%20results%20of%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20run%20a%20%E2%80%98Big%20Read%E2%80%99%20story%20with%20a%20headline%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F9fe88fba-6c0d-11e9-a9a5-351eeaef6d84%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%3A%20the%20WhatsApp%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20the%20most%20influential%20social%20media%20platform%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20it%20could%20also%20shape%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20time%20when%20WhatsApp%20restricted%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%98forwards%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20was%20elections%20in%20Brazil%20that%20caused%20it%20to%20enforce%20the%20restriction.%20Last%20year%20too%2C%20Brazilian%20authorities%20urged%20messaging%20platform%20WhatsApp%20to%20hold%20back%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20%E2%80%9CCommunities%E2%80%9D%20tool%20until%20elections%20were%20completed%20in%20October