%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13215256%2FUntitled-design-6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20colonel%20is%20among%20three%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20militant%20attack%20in%20south%20Kashmir%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2013%2C%20prompting%20the%20top%20security%20brass%20to%20rush%20to%20the%20area%20where%20a%20major%20search%20operation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20based%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%20was%20killed%20along%20with%20a%20young%20major-ranked%20officer%20and%20a%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20during%20the%20attack%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20terrorists%20had%20taken%20a%20strategically-advantageous%20position%20and%20opened%20fire%20relentlessly%20on%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20the%20Army%20near%20Ahlan%20Gadol%20water%20stream%2C%20giving%20the%20team%20little%20time%20to%20react%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGunfire%20during%20anti-insurgency%20operation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Army%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20an%20anti-insurgency%20operation%20was%20launched%20jointly%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20the%20Army%20in%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20September%2012%20and%2013%20following%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20intelligence%20on%20the%20presence%20of%20terrorists%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gadol%20area%20of%20Kokernag%2C%20some%2090%20km%20from%20the%20capital%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReports%20said%20that%20the%20operation%2C%20which%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20during%20the%20night%2C%20resumed%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20after%20security%20forces%20reportedly%20got%20a%20tip%20that%20the%20attackers%20were%20taking%20shelter%20in%20a%20hideout%20in%20a%20hilly%20area%20of%20Gadol%20village%2C%20which%20is%20situated%20amidst%20dense%20forests%20and%20thick%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20security%20forces%20moved%20towards%20the%20hideout%2C%20they%20came%20under%20heavy%20gunfire.%20Reports%20said%20that%20an%20Army%20colonel%20took%20the%20first%20shots%20followed%20by%20his%20deputy%2C%20a%20major-ranked%20officer%2C%20and%20a%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20three%20were%20critically%20injured%20in%20the%20initial%20firing%20and%20terrorists%20continued%20to%20fire%20in%20order%20to%20prevent%20the%20evacuation%20of%20the%20victims%20from%20the%20spot.%20However%2C%20an%20Army%20chopper%20was%20pressed%20into%20service%20and%20one%20of%20the%20victims%20was%20evacuated%20to%20a%20military%20hospital%20in%20Srinagar%20where%20he%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deceased%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Colonel%20Manpreet%20Singh%2C%20a%20recipient%20of%20Sena%20Medal%20in%202021%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20(DSP)%2C%20Humayun%20Muzamil%20Bhat%20and%20Major%20Aashish%20Dhonchak%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%20The%20bodies%20of%20Singh%20and%20Dhonchak%20have%20not%20been%20retrieved%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDSP%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20Ghulam%20Hassan%20Bhat%2C%20retired%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20as%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General.%20The%20younger%20Bhat%2C%20a%202018%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Police%20Service%20officer%2C%20had%20gotten%20married%20last%20year%20and%20has%20a%20two-month%20old%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20didn%E2%80%99t%20share%20more%20details%20about%20the%20deceased%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDilbag%20Singh%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20Rajiv%20Ghai%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20strategic%20Chinar%20Corps%20based%20in%20Srinagar%20which%20supervises%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20operations%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20arrived%20in%20Gadol%20along%20with%20other%20senior%20officers%20of%20security%20establishment%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20to%20assess%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20Pariwar%20DGP%20J%26amp%3BK%20Sh%20Dilbag%20Singh%20has%20condoled%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20the%20braveheart%20officers%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20Army%20in%20an%20encounter%20at%20Gadool%2CKokernag%2CAnantnag.%3Cbr%3EThe%20DGP%20has%20said%20in%20his%20message%20that%20he%20is%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20terrible%20loss%20of%20three%20young%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpMJSwYE8wX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FpMJSwYE8wX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20(%40JmuKmrPolice)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJmuKmrPolice%2Fstatus%2F1701995472859316533%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDGP%20Singh%20later%20led%20a%20wreath-laying%20ceremony%20for%20the%20slain%20police%20officer%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Secretary%20Arun%20Mehta%20and%20other%20officers%20of%20the%20civil%20and%20security%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20major%20search%20operation%20has%20been%20launched%20to%20track%20down%20the%20perpetrators%20with%20drones%20and%20choppers%20conducting%20aerial%20reconnaissance%20surveys%20around%20the%20forested%20areas%20of%20Gadol%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20any%20suspicious%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Resistance%20Front%2C%20which%20officials%20believe%20is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%2C%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Crevenge%20attack%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20several%20posts%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20Wire%2C%20however%2C%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoldier%20killed%20in%20Narla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20encounter%20took%20place%20more%20than%20a%20month%20after%20three%20army%20soldiers%20were%20gunned%20down%20in%20a%20forested%20area%20in%20the%20adjoining%20Kulgam%20district%20of%20south%20Kashmir.%20A%20Jaish-e-Mohammad-linked%20terror%20outfit%20had%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%20in%20which%20two%20more%20Army%20soldiers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20setback%20for%20security%20forces%20in%20Kokernag%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20Army%20gunned%20down%20two%20terrorists%20in%20Rajouri%20district%20of%20Jammu.%20An%20Army%20soldier%20was%20also%20killed%20in%20the%20operation%20in%20Narla%20village%20while%20three%20more%20soldiers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20initial%20exchange%20of%20gunfire%20in%20Rajouri%2C%20Kent%2C%20a%20six-year-old%20female%20Labrador%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20dog%20unit%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20died%20while%20trying%20to%20save%20her%20handler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20at%20least%2010%20Army%20soldiers%2C%20including%20five%20commandos%20of%20the%20elite%20para%20unit%20were%20killed%20in%20two%20separate%20attacks%20and%20encounters%20in%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%2C%20a%20region%20which%20remained%20free%20of%20terrorism%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorthern%20Army%20Commander%20Lieutenant%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20function%20at%20IIT%20Jammu%20that%20Pakistan%20was%20pushing%20foreign%20terrorists%20into%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20disrupt%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPakistan%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20efforts%20from%20its%20side%20to%20send%20foreign%20terrorists%20here%2C%20despite%20the%20better%20internal%20conditions%20(security%20