5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103641948.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFor%20avid%20movie%20lovers%20with%20a%20taste%20for%20diverse%20and%20compelling%20cinema%2C%20here's%20a%20curated%20list%20of%2010%20best%20international%20films%20that%20promise%20to%20captivate%20your%20imagination%20and%20take%20you%20on%20a%20cinematic%20journey%20around%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2F10-best-international-films-to-watch-for-movie-lovers%2Fphotostory%2F103641948.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'All%20Four%20Cases%20of%20Nipah%20Infections%20Are%20Each%20Other%E2%80%99s%20Contacts'%3A%20Kerala%20Epidemiologist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F10124700%2Fvirology.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20Kerala%20undergoes%20the%20fourth%20outbreak%20of%20Nipah%20virus%20since%202018%20which%20has%20already%20killed%20two%20and%20infected%20two%20more%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20kicked%20in%20protocols%20to%20make%20containment%20zones%20in%20Kozhikode%20district.%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20also%20sent%20an%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20team%20to%20the%20state.%20The%20village%20panchayats%2C%20where%20these%20four%20lived%2C%20have%20also%20stepped%20up%20surveillance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20state%20epidemiologist%20Dr.%20Hari%20Shankar%20said%20all%20the%20four%20people%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20are%20related%20to%2C%20or%20are%20contacts%20of%20the%20index(first)%20case.%20This%20explains%20how%20the%20virus%20can%20spread%20between%20humans%2C%20once%20it%20enters%20the%20human%20chain.%20Besides%20the%20four%20known%20cases%2C%20there%20are%20two%20more%20suspected%20ones%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20contact%20tracing%20is%20still%20going%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20out%20of%20the%20four%2C%20two%20are%20still%20undergoing%20treatment%20%5Band%20two%20have%20died%5D%2C%20we%20are%20speaking%20to%20their%20relatives%20to%20trace%20the%20history%20of%20their%20whereabouts%20for%20at%20least%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20so%20that%20further%20spread%20of%20the%20virus%20can%20be%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKerala%20experienced%20its%20first-ever%20and%20the%20worst%20outbreak%20of%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20in%20Kozhikode%20in%202018%2C%20when%20of%20the%2023%20infected%2C%20only%20two%20people%20survived.%20In%20that%20outbreak%20too%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20were%20related%20to%20the%20index%20case.%20The%20second%20and%20the%20third%20outbreaks%20were%20far%20less%20deadly%20than%20the%20first%20one.%20In%202019%2C%20one%20boy%20from%20Ernakulam%20district%20reported%20positive%20for%20the%20virus%20but%20no%20death%20took%20place.%20In%202021%2C%20one%20died%20in%20the%20outbreak%20in%20Kozhikode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fhow-kerala-passed-the-tough-nipah-test%5C%22%3EHow%20Kerala%20Passed%20the%20Tough%20Nipah%20Test%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com%2Farticles%2F10.1186%2Fs12879-021-05865-7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epaper%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Epublished%20in%202021%2C%20the%20researchers%20of%20National%20Institute%20of%20Virology%20(NIV)%20wrote%20that%20they%20had%20found%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPteropus%20medius%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20bats%2C%20or%20what%20are%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Indian%20fruit%20bats%2C%20were%20harbouring%20the%20Nipah%20virus.%20And%2C%20the%20spillover%20to%20the%20lone%20Nipah%20case%20of%20the%2021-year-old%20boy%20in%202019%20happened%20from%20the%20animal%20only.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20know%20what%20led%20to%20the%20spillover%20this%20time%2C%20ICMR%20and%20National%20Institute%20of%20Virology%20researchers%20are%20expected%20to%20arrive%20in%20Kerala%20soon%2C%20the%20state%20epidemiologist%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20paper%2C%20the%20researchers%20said%20that%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20was%20going%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CNiV%20%5BNipah%20virus%5D%20Positivity%20in%20Pteropus%20species%20of%20bats%20revealed%20that%20NiV%20is%20circulating%20in%20many%20districts%20of%20Kerala%20state%2C%20and%20active%20surveillance%20of%20NiV%20should%20be%20immediately%20set%20up%20to%20know%20the%20hotspot%20area%20for%20NiV%20infection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20was%20nonetheless%20able%20to%20limit%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20virus%20to%20a%20great%20extent%20in%202019%20and%202021%20taking%20lessons%20from%20the%202018%20outbreak%20after%20the%20spillover%20events%20from%20animals%20to%20humans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Fnipah-virus%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWorld%20Health%20Organisation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20virus%20is%20mostly%20found%20in%20bats%20or%20pigs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20NIV%2FICMR%20scientists%20are%20able%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20details%20of%20the%20spillover%20event%20this%20time%2C%20it%20would%20help%20us%20take%20precautionary%20measures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Shankar%20said.%20Although%20it%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20task%20to%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fthiruvananthapuram%2Fnipah-virus-alert-in-keralas-kozhikode-8935582%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20areas%20under%20surveillance%20in%20the%20current%20outbreak%20are%20two%20villages%20in%20the%20eastern%20region%20of%20the%20Kozhikode%20district.%20Both%20the%20villages%20are%20situated%2015%20km%20away%20from%20Changaroth%2C%20where%20the%20deadly%20outbreak%20of%202018%20happened.%20The%20region%20has%20dense%20forests%20where%20these%20bats%20are%20mostly%20found.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Shankar%20said%2C%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20September%2012%2C%20that%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20at%20the%20moment%20as%20to%20which%20of%20the%20two%20strains%20of%20the%20virus%20%E2%80%93%20Malaysian%20or%20Bangladeshi%20%E2%80%93%20was%20currently%20in%20circulation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20results%20of%20the%20genome%20sequencing%2C%20done%20to%20know%20this%2C%20are%20still%20awaited%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Incidentally%2C%20all%20three%20previous%20outbreaks%20were%20related%20to%20Bangladeshi%20strain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20WHO%2C%20there%20are%20mostly%20two%20strains%20of%20the%20virus%20%E2%80%93%20Bangladeshi%20and%20Malaysian.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20first%20recognized%20outbreak%20in%20Malaysia%20%5Bin%201999%5D%2C%20which%20also%20affected%20Singapore%2C%20most%20human%20infections%20resulted%20from%20direct%20contact%20with%20sick%20pigs%20or%20their%20contaminated%20tissues.%20Transmission%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20occurred%20via%20unprotected%20exposure%20to%20secretions%20from%20the%20pigs%2C%20or%20unprotected%20contact%20with%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20sick%20animal%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20WHO%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20consumption%20of%20certain%20fruits%20or%20fruit%20products%2C%20which%20have%20been%20contaminated%20with%20saliva%20or%20secretions%20of%20fruit%20bats%2C%20that%20harboured%20the%20virus%2C%20led%20to%20the%20outbreaks.%20In%20all%20the%20previous%20three%20outbreaks%20of%20the%20virus%20in%20Kerala%2C%20fruit%20bats%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20the%20source%20which%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanimalia.bio%2Findian-flying-fox%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20breed%20between%20July%20and%20October%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20thus%20the%20chances%20of%20them%20infecting%20raw%20fruits%20become%20higher%20in%20this%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20the%20symptoms%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20respiratory.%20And%2C%20therefore%2C%20the%20spread%20from%20one%20person%20to%20another%20is%20quite%20noticeable%20unless%20the%20containment%20measures%20are%20not%20quickly%20put%20in%20place.%20Some%20patients%20also%20develop%20neurological%20complications%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20death.%20Those%20who%20died%20in%20the%20current%20outbreak%20had%20both%20neurological%20and%20respiratory%20symptoms%2C%20the%20state%20epidemiologist%20said.%20While%20one%20died%20on%20August%2030%2C%20the%20other%20passed%20away%20on%20September%2011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20like%20the%20vaccine%2C%20there%20is%20currently%20no%20proven%20treatment%20for%20the%20disease%20per%20se%2C%20according%20to%20the%20WHO.%20The%20symptomatic%20treatment%20is%2C%20however%2C%20available%20although%20the%20state%20epidemiologist%20said%20they%20are%20using%20antivirals%20and%20monoclonal%20antibodies%20to%20treat%20those%20infected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694619009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F10124700%2Fvirology.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fall-four-cases-of-nipah-infections-are-each-others-contacts-kerala-ep