on%2C%20repair%2C%20maintenance%20%26amp%3B%20beautification%20of%20roads%20in%20the%20capital.%20These%20central%20funds%20were%20used%20by%20PWD%20%26amp%3B%20MCD%20for%20the%20makeover.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPWD%20and%20MCD%20comes%20under%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20power%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20done%20by%20these%20agencies%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20quoting%20today%20was%20undertaken%20through%20the%20funds%20of%20the%20Central%20Govt.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20evident%20that%20unless%20paid%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20Delhi%20govt%20won%E2%80%99t%20work.%20So%2C%20work%20is%20paid%20for%20and%20done%20by%20Centre%2C%20table%20is%20attached%20for%20all%20to%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lekhi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmea-gets-rs-18050-crore-in-union-budget-for-2023-24%2Farticleshow%2F97531042.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPress%20Trust%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20allocated%20Rs%20990%20crore%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20after%20opposition%20parties%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20overspending%20by%20three-times%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%E2%80%99s%20press%20information%20bureau%20fact%20check%20unit%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20these%20claims%20are%20misleading.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20a%20tweet%20by%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20that%20said%20the%20government%20had%20spent%20300%25%20more%20than%20the%20budget%2C%20the%20PIB%20said%20that%20this%20claim%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmisleading%E2%80%9D%20but%20did%20not%20mention%20how%20it%20was%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20tweet%20claims%20Govt%20spent%20300%25%20more%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FG20%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23G20%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20funds%20allocated%20in%20budget%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPIBFactCheck%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PIBFactCheck%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E1%20This%20claim%20is%20misleading%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2%20The%20quoted%20expenditure%20is%20majorly%20towards%20permanent%20asset%20creation%20by%20ITPO%20%26amp%3B%20other%20infrastructure%20development%20which%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20hosting%20G20%20Summit%20alone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCRGkraJw3J%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCRGkraJw3J%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20PIB%20Fact%20Check%20(%40PIBFactCheck)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPIBFactCheck%2Fstatus%2F1701158567561351498%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20quoted%20expenditure%20is%20majorly%20towards%20permanent%20asset%20creation%20by%20ITPO%20%26amp%3B%20other%20infrastructure%20development%20which%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20hosting%20G20%20Summit%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PIB%20fact%20check%20unit%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20look%20at%20the%20spending%20by%20other%20countries%20that%20have%20hosted%20G20%20summits%20in%20the%20past%20shows%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20expenditure%20of%20over%20Rs%204%2C110%20crore%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20Lekhi%2C%20stands%20more%20than%20other%20host%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20local%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fekonomi.bisnis.com%2Fread%2F20221020%2F10%2F1589875%2Fanggaran-g20-tembus-rp674-miliar-berapa-manfaatnya-untuk-perekonomian%5C%22%3E%3Csp