20get%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ravindra%20bought%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20in%20Amravati.%20With%20a%20bank%20loan%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20he%20expanded%20the%20farm%20with%204%2C000%20hens.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20then%2C%20I%20started%20earning%20well%20from%20the%20business%20and%20got%20my%20%3Cem%3Ekachaa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehouse%20renovated.%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20expanded%20the%20farm%20to%2012%2C000%20hens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20happiness%20was%20short-lived.%20In%202006%2C%20India%20witnessed%20an%20outbreak%20of%20bird%20flu%20that%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20poultry%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20first%20bird%20flu%20in%20the%20country.%20People%20were%20scared%20to%20consume%20broilers%20and%20eggs.%20They%20even%20forced%20poultry%20farmers%20to%20kill%20their%20birds.%20I%20sold%2016%2C000%20broilers%20for%20Rs%202%E2%80%933%20per%20kg%2C%20which%20were%20earlier%20sold%20at%20Rs%2050%E2%80%9360%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329823%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20thankfully%2C%20I%20already%20had%20bought%2015-acre%20land%20to%20practise%20farming.%20So%20for%20those%20two%20years%2C%20I%20continued%20to%20earn%20by%20growing%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20like%20oranges%2C%20soybean%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Etuar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pigeon%20pea)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20he%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20a%20bank%20and%20restarted%20the%20business%20with%2020%2C000%20egg-laying%20hens.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20profits%2C%20I%20kept%20on%20increasing%20the%20birds%20at%20my%20farm.%20Today%2C%20I%20have%201.8%20lakh%20hens%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravindra%2C%20who%20has%20been%20doing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54545%2Fwomen-farmers-empowerment-fighting-maharashtra-drought%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoultry%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20he%20now%20earns%20up%20to%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20day%20through%20this%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESharing%20learnings%20with%20new%20IAS%20officers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies%20like%20indoor%20vertical%20farming%2C%20greenhouse%20farming%2C%20automatic%20watering%2C%20drip%20systems%2C%20remote%20sensing%20irrigation%20systems%2C%20and%20organic%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20employed%20only%2050%20workers%20to%20manage%20my%20poultry%20farm%20spread%20across%2050%20acres.%20Most%20of%20the%20work%20is%20automated.%20For%20example%2C%20from%20collecting%20eggs%20from%20broilers%20and%20giving%20feed%20to%20poultry%20birds%2C%20to%20collecting%20their%20excreta%2C%20everything%20is%20ensured%20using%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%202013%2C%20he%20was%20selected%20by%20the%20state%20government%20as%20one%20of%20the%2080%20progressive%20farmers%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20Europe%20for%20a%2010-day%20trip%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20expanding%20the%20farming%20business%20with%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20also%20conferred%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Jagjivan%20Ram%20Abhinav%20Kisan%20Puraskar%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329819%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20also%20conferred%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Jagjivan%20Ram%20Abhinav%20Kisan%20Puraskar%20by%20the%20ICAR.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20he%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Vasantrao%20Naik%20Award%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20Government.%20Later%20in%202021%2C%20he%20received%20the%20Innovative%20Farmer%20Award%20from%20the%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute%20(IARI).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20also%20conferred%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Jagjivan%20Ram%20Abhinav%20Kisan%20Puraskar%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20because%20of%20these%20awards%20that%20Ravindra%20says%20that%20he%20was%20able%20to%20establish%20an%20identity%20and%20free%20himself%20from%20corrupt%20officers%20at%20the%20grassroots.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20local%20officers%20used%20to%20come%20to%20me%20to%20get%20hens%20and%20eggs%20for%20free%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%20If%20denied%2C%20they%20would%20provoke%20neighbours%20to%20complain%20against%20me%20for%20bad%20odour%20coming%20from%20my%20poultry%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20Government%20announces%20compensation%20when%20farmers%20experience%20crop%20losses.%20For%20this%2C%20%3Cem%3Epatwari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(village%20registrar)%20is%20appointed%20to%20survey%20the%20damage.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20seek%20a%20share%20in%20the%20compensation%20amount.%20If%20somebody%20refuses%20to%20give%20the%20amount%2C%20they%20remove%20their%20names%20from%20the%20list.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavindra%20says%20he%20was%20able%20to%20highlight%20these%20challenges%20in%20front%20of%20IAS%20trainees%20at%20LBSNAA.%20He%20also%20advised%20them%20to%20not%20rely%20on%20junior%20officers%20only%2C%20and%20to%20visit%20farmers%E2%80%99%20sites%20on%20their%20own%20to%20understand%20the%20challenges%20at%20the%20grassroots%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20progress%20with%20farming%20alone.%20After%20sowing%2C%20it%20takes%20five%20months%20to%20generate%20income%20from%20the%20crop.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20they%20are%20left%20without%20any%20means%20to%20earn.%20So%2C%20officers%20should%20encourage%20farmers%20to%20adopt%20parallel%20businesses%20like%20poultry%20farming%2C%20mushroom%20farming%2C%20silk%20and%20cattle%20rearing%2C%20and%20vermicompost%20business%20to%20boost%20their%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavindra%20shares%20that%20it%20was%20crucial%20for%20him%20to%20put%20forward%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20expectations%20to%20these%20future%20officers%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20have%20received%20this%20opportunity%20felt%20like%20a%20great%20achievement.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20LBSNAA%2C%20reputed%20officers%20lecture%20the%20IAS%20trainees.%20And%20that%20day%2C%20a%20farmer%20was%20able%20to%20take%20the%20stage.%20I%20hope%20with%20my%20work%2C%20younger%20generations%20do%20not%20feel%20hesitant%20to%20seek%20a%20career%20in%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Ravindra%20Metkar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694613032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-2-1694610828.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Starting%20poultry%20farming%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20today%2C%20Ravindra%20Metkar%20(55)%20owns%201.8%20lakh%20hens%20on%20his%20farm%20spread%20across%2050%20acres%20in%20Amravati%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20earning%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20day.%20The%20poultry%20farmer%20was%20invited%20to%20share%20his%20success%20story%20with%20189%20IAS%20trainees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329814%2Famravati-ravindra-metkar-poultry-farmer-success-story-lecture-ias-trainees-lbsnaa-mussoorie%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Journalist's%20Arrest%20in%20Bengal%20Points%20to%20the%20State's%20Worsening%20Media%20Freedom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13190430%2FScreenshot-2023-09-13-at-7.04.23-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKolkata%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20The%20recent%20arrest%20of%20journalist%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%20has%20once%20again%20cast%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20state%20of%20media%20freedom%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%2C%20a%20seasoned%20journalist%20with%20a%20decade-long%20association%20with%20the%20leading%20Bengali%20daily%2C%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPatrika%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20arrested%20from%20his%20residence%20on%20the%20night%20of%20September%206%2C%20following%20a%20police%20inquiry.%20Some%20opposition%20parties%E2%80%99%20versions%20have%20it%20that%20police%20visited%20Bagchi%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2028%20and%2029%2C%20presumably%20to%20question%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20paper%20did%20not%20report%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20on%20the%20frontpage.%20Many%20have%20pointed%20to%20the%20relative%20silence%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20media%20landscape%20over%20the%20arrest%2C%20questioning%20if%20it%20is%20the%20result%20of%20an%20unofficial%20gag%20order%20of%20sorts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20his%20investigative%20reports%20on%20illegal%20liquor%20traders%20in%20Kharagpur.%20These%20reports%20were%20published%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPatrika%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20August%2026%20and%2027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20and%20his%20source%2C%20one%20Basanti%20Das%2C%20were%20arrested%20and%20charged%20%E2%80%93%20among%20other%20sections%20%E2%80%93%20under%20Section%203(1)(r)(s)%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989.%20This%20section%20that%20deals%20with%20the%20intentional%20humiliation%20of%20individuals%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20or%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20within%20public%20view%20and%20carries%20non-bailable%20charges.%20Both%20were%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody%20for%2010%20days%2C%20with%20the%20next%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20September%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdivasi%20Bikash%20Parishad%2C%20a%20body%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20has%20strongly%20criticised%20the%20invocation%20of%20this%20charge%20in%20this%20case.%20Tez%20Kumar%20Toppo%2C%20the%20executive%20president%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20this%20section%20is%20meant%20to%20reduce%20torture%20on%20us%2C%20its%20implementation%20is%20often%20lacking%20when%20we%20call%20for%20it.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20misuse%20this%20section%20at%20their%20own%20will.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20largely%20believed%20that%20the%20story%20of%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20came%20to%20light%20after%20this%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20arrest%20was%20in%20an%20FIR%20filed%20after%20one%20Saraswati%20Singh%20of%20Kharagpur%20had%20filed%20a%20complaint%20on%20August%2028%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20second%20part%20of%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20report%20was%20published.%20Singh%20said%20that%20Bagchi%20and%20Das%20had%20used%20derogatory%20language%2C%20used%20caste-based%20insults%2C%20and%20attempted%20to%20disrobe%20her.%20Singh%20is%20reported%20to%20be%20acquainted%20with%20one%20of%20the%20people%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20report%20identifies%20as%20an%20illegal%20liquor%20trader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20has%20been%20working%20for%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20editor%20of%20the%20daily%2C%20Ishani%20Dutta%20Roy%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20with%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%20and%20in%20full%20support%20of%20free%20press%20and%20freedom%20of%20the%20press.%20Our%20stand%20is%20evident%20from%20what%20we%20are%20carrying%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBackground%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20backdrop%20to%20this%20incident%20is%20the%20ongoing%20tension%20between%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPatrika%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20government.%20Recently%2C%20the%20newspaper%20published%20a%20series%20of%20reports%20on%20the%20job%20recruitment%20scam%2C%20drawing%20from%20investigating%20agency%20findings%20that%20indirectly%20pointed%20to%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20nephew%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20national%20president%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20in%20various%20corruption%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20editorials%20have%20been%20sharp%20in%20their%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20incidents%20related%20to%20the%20panchayat%20polls%20and%20allegations%20of%20opposition%20intimidation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Calcutta%20Press%20Club%20has%20issued%20an%20official%20statement%20expressing%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20arrest.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Calcutta%20Press%20Club%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20arrest%20of%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%20and%20has%20sought%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20who%20has%20assured%2C%20due%20law%20will%20be%20followed%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20administration%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20dealing%20with%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20with%20a%20heavy%20hand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20highly%20placed%20executive%20at%20the%20publication%20revealed%20that%20the%20state%20government%20consistently%20issues%20veiled%20threats%20regarding%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20advertisements%20%E2%80%93%20a%20critical%20source%20of%20revenue%20for%20vernacular%20publications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20April%202022