and%20protect%20the%20fourth%20pillar%20of%20democracy%20and%20oblige.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20in%20a%20long%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20highlighted%20the%20chronology%20of%20the%20event.%20Adhikari%20was%20denied%20permission%20to%20meet%20Bagchi%20in%20Medinipur%20jail%2C%20with%20the%20superintendent%20citing%20that%20his%20name%20was%20not%20on%20the%20list%20of%20approved%20interviewers%20provided%20by%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESemi%20Emergency%20like%20situation%20in%20West%20Bengal%20under%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Authoritarian%20Regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20raised%20my%20voice%20earlier%20in%20my%20X-Handle%20when%20Mamata%20Police%20arrested%20Anandabazar%20Patrika%E2%80%99s%20Kharagpur%20Correspondent%3B%20Shri%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%2C%20for%20highlighting%20the%20menace%20of%20Hooch%20Traders%20in%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJYf9GeMRrV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJYf9GeMRrV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20%E2%80%A2%20%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%AD%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%81%20%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%A7%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%80%20(%40SuvenduWB)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSuvenduWB%2Fstatus%2F1701120453727981990%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECPI(M)%20leader%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%20criticised%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20priorities%2C%20alleging%20that%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20law%20and%20order%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20administration%20was%20preoccupied%20with%20arresting%20journalists%2C%20thereby%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20true%20state%20of%20media%20freedom%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-twe