e%20reports%20on%20illegal%20liquor%20trade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbengal-press-freedom-journalist-arrest-debmalya-bagchi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Journalist's%20Arrest%20in%20Bengal%20Points%20to%20the%20State's%20Worsening%20Media%20Freedom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKolkata%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20The%20recent%20arrest%20of%20journalist%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%20has%20once%20again%20cast%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20state%20of%20media%20freedom%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%2C%20a%20seasoned%20journalist%20with%20a%20decade-long%20association%20with%20the%20leading%20Bengali%20daily%2C%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPatrika%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20arrested%20from%20his%20residence%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2028%20and%2029%2C%20following%20a%20police%20inquiry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20paper%20did%20not%20report%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20on%20the%20frontpage.%20Many%20have%20pointed%20to%20the%20relative%20silence%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20media%20landscape%20over%20the%20arrest%2C%20questioning%20if%20it%20is%20the%20result%20of%20an%20unofficial%20gag%20order%20of%20sorts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20his%20investigative%20reports%20on%20illegal%20liquor%20traders%20in%20Kharagpur.%20These%20reports%20were%20published%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPatrika%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20August%2026%20and%2027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20and%20his%20source%2C%20one%20Basanti%20Das%2C%20were%20arrested%20and%20charged%20%E2%80%93%20among%20other%20sections%20%E2%80%93%20under%20Section%203(1)(r)(s)%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989.%20This%20section%20th