support%20of%20free%20press%20and%20freedom%20of%20the%20press.%20Our%20stand%20is%20evident%20from%20what%20we%20are%20carrying%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBackground%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20backdrop%20to%20this%20incident%20is%20the%20ongoing%20tension%20between%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPatrika%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20government.%20Recently%2C%20the%20newspaper%20published%20a%20series%20of%20reports%20on%20the%20job%20recruitment%20scam%2C%20drawing%20from%20investigating%20agency%20findings%20that%20indirectly%20pointed%20to%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20nephew%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20national%20president%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20in%20various%20corruption%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20editorials%20have%20been%20sharp%20in%20their%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20incidents%20related%20to%20the%20panchayat%20polls%20and%20allegations%20of%20opposition%20intimidation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Calcutta%20Press%20Club%20has%20issued%20an%20official%20statement%20expressing%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20arrest.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Calcutta%20Press%20Club%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20arrest%20of%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%20and%20has%20sought%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20who%20has%20assured%2C%20due%20law%20will%20be%20followed%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20administration%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20dealing%20with%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20with%20a%20heavy%20hand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20highly%20placed%20executive%20at%20the%20publication%20revealed%20that%20the%20state%20government%20consistently%20issues%20veiled%20threats%20regarding%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20advertisement