2%3A%22%3Cp%3EPicture%20this%20%E2%80%93%20every%20Friday%2C%20students%20of%20the%20Akshar%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307292%2Futtam-teron-parijat-academy-free-education-skill-development-for-poor-children-assam-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESchool%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%20congregate%20like%20eco-warriors%20on%20a%20mission.%20They%20arrive%2C%20bearing%20a%20week%E2%80%99s%20worth%20of%20collected%20plastic%2C%20their%20hands%20and%20pockets%20filled%20with%20discarded%20bottles%2C%20wrappers%2C%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20the%20lush%20green%20area%20of%20Pamohi%20locality%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20school%20does%20not%20want%20its%20pupils%20to%20compensate%20them%20with%20money.%20Instead%2C%20they%20only%20accept%20plastic%20in%20the%20form%20of%20fees!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20Parmita%20Sarma%20and%20Mazin%20Mukhtar%20in%202016%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20verdant%20paradise%2C%20this%20school%20has%20successfully%20turned%20education%20into%20an%20adventure%2C%20and%20fees%20into%20a%20pledge%20for%20a%20brighter%2C%20more%20sustainable%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20coming%20generation%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F218760%2Findian-womens-cricket-team-t20-world-cup-final-inspiring-shafali-verma-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20sections%20break%20the%20circle%20of%20poverty%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20be%20environmentally%20sensitive.%20Education%20is%20the%20only%20way%20these%20goals%20can%20be%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmita%20Sarma%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Akshar%20School%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20collected%20and%20recycled%20about%201%2C200%20bottles%20and%206%2C43%2C600%20plastic%20