-image-4-1694607097-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-4-1694607097-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329787%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20land%20on%20which%20the%20school%20is%20built%20was%20donated%20by%20Parmita%E2%80%99s%20mother.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Parmita%20Sarma%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202013%20when%20Parmita%20was%20in%20Lakhimpur%20to%20work%20for%20Bhupen%20Hazarika%2C%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20legendary%20singer%20and%20social%20worker%2C%20when%20she%20met%20Mazin.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20conversations%20at%20Bhupun%20Hazarika%E2%80%99s%20school%2C%20we%20realised%20how%20we%20both%20wanted%20to%20open%20a%20school%20that%20helps%20underprivileged%20children%20get%20access%20to%20quality%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20laid%20the%20seeds%20for%20the%20foundation%20of%20Akshar%20School.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20we%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20purchase%20land%20and%20build%20a%20school%20from%20scratch.%20It%20was%20my%20mother%20who%20donated%20the%20land%20and%20some%20funds%20to%20start%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20today%20is%20located%20in%20Pamohi%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326708%2Fdattu-agarwal-free-residential-school-for-girls-with-visual-impairment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20offers%20free%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20students.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20just%2010%20students%20as%20the%20villagers%20did%20not%20want%20their%20kids%20to%20study.%20Instead%2C%20they%20wanted%20them%20to%20work.%20It%20took%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20convincing%20to%20get%20even%20those%20ten%20kids%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%20the%2