nth%2C%20recalls%20his%20experience%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20curriculum%20was%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20what%20I%E2%80%99d%20experienced%20in%20my%20previous%20school.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20just%20interested%20in%20filling%20our%20heads%20with%20facts%3B%20they%20were%20dedicated%20to%20nurturing%20our%20holistic%20growth.%20And%20the%20best%20part%20is%20that%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20ask%20for%20a%20single%20rupee%20in%20fees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20feature%20of%20their%20curriculum%20is%20that%20the%20school%20focuses%20on%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20when%20they%20step%20out%20of%20here%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20world.%20We%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20vocational%20training-based%20courses%20for%20the%20kids%20to%20learn.%20We%20teach%20them%20carpentry%2C%20solar%20panel%20fitting%2C%20electrical%20work%2C%20tailoring%2C%20gardening%2C%20and%20landscaping%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20philosophy%20is%20%E2%80%98Learning%20by%20Doing%E2%80%99%20and%20this%20curriculum%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do%2C%20the%20couple%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecycling%20Plastic%20Into%20Substantial%20Goods%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20set%20up%20a%20recycling%20plant%20on%20the%20campus.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plant%20recycles%20as%20much%20plastic%20that%20is%20recyclable%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20eco-bricks.%20Our%20kids%20learn%20how%20to%20convert%20plastic%20into%20bricks%20and%20work%20in%20the%20plant%20after%20school.%20We%20pay%20them%20for%20that%20too.%20This%20way%20they%20get%20to%20learn%20an%20extra%20skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20eco-bricks%20are%20then%20used%20in%20smaller%20constructions%20in%20and%20around%20the%20school.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20using%20a%20machine%20from%20the%20Netherlands.%20The%20machine%20up