0000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-guinness-world-records_6283457.jpg%3F20230913133215%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fguinness-world-records-astronauts-jugglers-and-cuddly-toys-who-has-made-it-into-the-book-for-2024-12960510%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20people%20have%20at%20some%20point%20considered%20how%20they%20might%20want%20to%20make%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fguinness-world-records-astronauts-jugglers-and-cuddly-toys-who-has-made-it-into-the-book-for-2024-12960510%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fguinness-world-records-astronauts-jugglers-and-cuddly-toys-who-has-made-it-into-the-book-for-2024-12960510%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fguinness-world-records-astronauts-jugglers-and-cuddly-toys-who-has-made-it-into-the-book-for-2024-12960510%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20U-Turn%20After%20Backlash%2C%20Centre%20Mulls%20Lifting%20Curbs%20on%20Import%20of%20Personal%20Computers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13173221%2Fglenn-carstens-peters-npxXWgQ33ZQ-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20U-turn%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20considering%20launching%20a%20new%20registration%20system%20for%20the%20import%20of%20personal%20computers%20without%20any%20quota%20and%20licensing%20requirements%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fleeway-in-laptop-personal-computers-import-curbs-give-oems-a-breather-123091201049_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20on%20August%203%20had%20issued%20a%20notification%20announcing%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20import%20of%20personal%20computers%2C%20laptops%2C%20and%20tablets%20without%20a%20license%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20to%20prevent%20Chinese%20imports%20from%20flooding%20Indian%20markets%20and%20to%20promote%20local%20manufacturing.%20The%20notification%20had%20put%20the%20import%20of%20these%20devices%20under%20a%20strict%20licensing%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20(DGFT)%20had%20received%20a%20severe%20backlash%2C%20with%20traders%20expressing%20fear%20that%20it%20would%20result%20in%20an%20extreme%20shortfall%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20availability%20of%20computer%20products%20in%20the%20market%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20festive%20season%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apprehensions%20of%20traders%20are%20substantiated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%2080%25%20of%20laptops%20in%20the%20country%20are%20imported%2C%20with%20China%20contributing%20to%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share.%20Only%20one-third%20of%20personal%20computer%20devices%20sold%20in%20India%20are%20assembled%20locally.%20Under%20pressure%20from%20traders%2C%20the%20government%20had%20extended%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20ban%2C%20changing%20it%20from%20%E2%80%98immediate%20effect%E2%80%99%20to%20October%2031%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImport%20consignments%20can%20be%20cleared%20till%20October%2031%2C%202023%2C%20without%20a%20license%20for%20restricted%20imports.%20For%20clearance%20of%20import%20consignments%20with%20effect%20from%20November%201%2C%202023%2C%20a%20valid%20license%20for%20restricted%20imports%20is%20required%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20had%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fgovt-defers-implementation-order-of-restrictions-on-imports-of-laptops-computers-till-october-31%2F1701560%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20traders%20still%20weren%E2%80%99t%20happy%2C%20essentially%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20ban%20given%20that%20local%20manufacturing%20isn%E2%80%99t%20anywhere%20close%20to%20meeting%20the%20demand%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20latest%20news%20of%20instituting%20a%20new%20registration%20system%2C%20traders%20say%2C%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20an%20effort%20by%20the%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cget%20out%20of%20a%20hole%E2%80%9D%20that%20it%20has%20dug%20itself%20into%2C%20without%20factoring%20in%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20has%20dug%20themselves%20a%20hole%20and%20now%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20out%20of%20it.%20They%20realised%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20be%20gained%20from%20setting%20the%20deadline%20in%20November.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20viable%20for%20companies%20to%20shift%20their%20manufacturing%20units%20to%20India%20on%20such%20short%20notice.%20Unless%20they%20give%20at%20least%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20possible%20for%20companies%20to%20start%20manufacturing%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20an%20original%20equipment%20manufacturer%20(OEM)%20as%20saying.%20In%20business%20parlance%2C%20an%20OEM%20means%C2%A0a%20company%20that%20makes%20a%20product%20to%20be%20sold%20by%20another%20company%20under%20its%20own%20name.%20For%20instance%2C%20an%20OEM%20computer%20manufacturer%20might%20make%20computers%20for%20a%20brand%20like%20Dell%20or%20Lenovo%2C%20who%20then%20sell%20the%20products%20under%20their%20own%20brand%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20latest%20news%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20sigh%20of%20relief%20on%20the%20part%20of%20OEMs%20like%20Apple%2C%20HP%2C%20Dell%2C%20and%20Lenovo%2C%20who%20have%20been%20busy%20ramping%20up%20their%20imports%20in%20view%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20festive%20season%20when%20sales%20are%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20huge%20spike.%20The%20possible%20change%20in%20the%20rules%20would%20also%20mean%20that%20there%20would%20not%20be%20any%20shortfall%20in%20the%20supply.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20feeling%20among%20traders%20that%2C%20despite%20the%20changed%20norms%2C%20the%20chaos%20and%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20uncertainty%20engendered%20by%20the%20government%20could%20result%20in%20a%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImports%20have%20been%20going%20smoothly%20for%20now%2C%20and%20continue%20to%20remain%20so%20if%20new%20registration%20is%20put%20in%20place.%20The%20move%20has%20given%20us%20some%20breathing%20space.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty.%20Conversation%20about%20this%20is%20still%20ongoing%20and%20there%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20any%20official%20word%20from%20the%20government%20on%20when%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20PC%20manufacturer%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20government%20would%20only%20monitor%20the%20source%20and%20value%20of%20devices%20as%20part%20of%20an%20import%20management%20system%20for%20the%20current%20financial%20year.%20The%20quota%20and%20other%20compliance%20requirements%20would%20come%20into%20play%20only%20in%20the%20next%20financial%20year%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20consumer%20that%20such%20an%20allowance%20has%20been%20made.%20Otherwise%2C%20companies%20would%20have%20resorted%20to%20hoarding%20and%20selling%20devices%20at%20exorbitant%20prices.%20People%20would%20also%20be%20getting%20older%20devices%2C%20which%20would%20be%20sold%20to%20them%20at%20a%20premium%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Faisal%20Kawoosa%2C%20founder%20and%20chief%20analyst%20at%20Techarc%2C%20a%20market%20research%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694606848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13173221%2Fglenn-carstens-peters-npxXWgQ33ZQ-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-a-fac